body.name: Nightstand with Charging Station and LED Lights, LED Night Stand with 2 USB Ports and 2 AC Outlets, Modern End Table with 3 Drawers, Bedside Table with Open Storage for Bedroom, Rustic Brown
features: 【LED Light with multi-variable RGB colors】The bedside nightstand comes with beautiful Multi-colour RGB LED Light, Phone App + Key multiple control modes. You can freely set the color, brightness, music mode and timing function, and design your light show according to needs and scenes. The colorful lighting design of the side table brings a warm and stylish dreamy atmosphere to decorating your bedroom or living room.

【Nightstand with Charging Station】Unlike other ordinary nightstands, this nightstand comes with 2 Standard Plug Outlets and 2 USB Ports that allow you to charge your phone, laptop and other devices at the same time. A 4.9ft long power supply cord allows you to place your end table in most places. Whether you want to get a set and use them together to coordinate the space or use them separately for more convenience, it depends on you!

【Large Capacity to Save Space】The night stand has 3 sliding drawers, top shelf, and 1 middle shelf. The large capacity of the drawers can offer plenty of space for organizing small items. And the tabletop and open space is convenient for the daily use. The top shelf is designed for simple storage, placing glasses, small items or your cell phone that is charging. The end side table surface is enclosed on the three sides edge protection, which protect the cups or valuables from dropping. Suitable for any room, such as bedroom, living room.

【Sturdy & Durable End Table】Made of high-quality particleboard and metal material, thick and durable enough to strongly support the end table itself and stuff inside or on it. The board is easy to clean, waterproof and scratch resistant. Meanwhile, our nightstand is equipped with 4 adjustable metal legs, provides a long lifetime to use, good looking and durable. Overall dimension: 15.7"D x 17.7" W x 34.6"H. The tabletop of this nightstand can support up to 44 lbs, the top shelf can hold up to 11 lbs and the drawers can hold up to 22 lbs.

【Easy to Assemble & Risk Free Purchase】All labeled pieces, tools and step-by-step installation manual are included in the package, you can easily assemble this amazing nightstand within 30 minutes. Feel free to email us if you have any questions or concerns, our 24-hour professional customer service team is always here to help you.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 5, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Takes a little while to assemble

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 19, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Really cute and perfect for organization
reviews.reviewText: The nightstand is actually pretty cute and seems pretty durable for the price which is good, assembly is a bit long and you’re definitely gonna need two people for it, there were only one or two holes that didn’t perfectly align while assembling but I just drilled it in a bit and it works perfect! I love the lights on it and how there’s a lot of different storage/organization spaces. The hooks included are great for keeping stuff off the surface as well to help declutter (which was a major issue with my old nightstand) overall pretty good for the price and would definitely recommend. :)

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy assembling & pretty to look at
reviews.reviewText: I love this nightstand. It was very easy to put together with the tools I keep in the house, just a Philips screw driver is all I needed. If you can read and follow the instructions it goes together quick and easy. I'm 55 years old and do not have an engineering degree.I love the organized space it provides, the lighting, outlets etc... room for everything. A great piece for a reasonable price. I would recommend to a friend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars U Buy It, You put it together
reviews.reviewText: There was a couple typos in the directions provided. Ultimately I was able to get it together but you are putting every piece together if you buy this item. Also, the lighting strip doesn't stick long I have caught mine hanging off a couple times. I have other items that I have buggy with lighting strips that really stick. However the light on this item function perfectly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for CPAP users!
reviews.reviewText: As long as you understand that you're buying dorm room style furniture made from particleboard and not any kind of fine furniture, you'll probably be pleased with this.It took me almost 2 hours to assemble the first one. The second was cut to 1.5 hours since I knew what I was doing then. The instructions (pictorial only) were good, but not great.Every piece fit perfectly where it was supposed to and once completed it seems quite sturdy. I would avoid putting anything heavy on the little raised upper shelf. I left the LED light strips off, as I found them kind of silly.I've had a good quality night stand for years, but once I had to start using a CPAP, it drove me crazy. The CPAP took most of the top of my nightstand, with a hose hanging down in front of the drawers. This inexpensive nightstand - though noticeably smaller than what I had before, is much better. The CPAP fits neatly in the space under the top drawer, the hose comes out the side, and the mask hangs perfectly on one of the hooks off the side. So the top of this night stand neatly holds my books, phone, iPad, glasses, etc., and I have easy access to the drawers because the hose is on the side.

reviews.reviewText: This is the worst manufactured piece of crap I’ve ever had to put together! The directions are ridiculous, the many pieces do not line up with the pre drilled holes.
